Package org.loudouncodes.jkarel

Interface MapDataSource

public interface MapDataSource
The abstract concept of a 'source' for map data. When this interface was first extracted, only the xml parser for map files implemented it. There are plans to have implementations of maze generating algorithms from the book "mazes for programmers" implement this interface, and who knows what other sources of map data there could be in the future... That's the whole point of an interface, we are leaving the door open for future developers to plug in ideas we haven't even thought of yet.
